Recommends: python3-venv
Suggests: conda
Description: GUI tool for managing Isaac Lab training sessions
 A PyQt5-based graphical interface for managing Isaac Lab
 training and play sessions. Features include:
 .
 - Workspace scanning and task discovery
 - Conda/venv environment management
 - Train/Play mode with parameter configuration
 - tmux session management for training processes
 - Checkpoint resume and model loading
 - Multi-language support (Chinese/English)
 - Support for multiple RL algorithms (rsl_rl, sb3, skrl, rl_games)